    "description": "<strong>Billionaire Tim Martin, known by many as &quot;Tiny Man&quot;, had an unfortunate encounter with a blue-collar worker who turned out to be a notorious villain. </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349060/extras/dccae474bc0e49def6365b9e3808b286.avif?t=1770948904\" width=640 height=354 /></span><br><strong>As a result, Tim not only lost his soup but also his height, leaving him vulnerable and exposed. </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349060/extras/e2ed9ca414b18151ce2860b841c54ca4.avif?t=1770948904\" width=640 height=354 /></span><br><strong>It was a humbling experience for the once-arrogant businessman, and he couldn't help but wonder what other surprises life had in store for him if had had his soup. <br>Despite his setback, Tim vowed to bounce back stronger and wiser, determined to reclaim his throne in the world of his delicious treat.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349060/extras/1f5d5df545f66cbc5826852c5221e331.avif?t=1770948904\" width=640 height=354 /></span><br><br><strong>Tim Martin shrugs off his loss of height but cries over his lost soup. <br>He embarks on an epic adventure into an innocent, yet sinister man's house, <br>using his skills in Glide, Climb, and Dodge to steal everything he can. <br>With his haul, he hopes to afford his beloved soup once again.<br><br>Tiny Man's Revenge is an action-packed game where you play as a tiny person with the goal of stealing everything in a house. <br>Realistic movements make the gameplay immersive, and multiple endings depend on your decisions throughout. <br>The game provides a thrilling experience with its action-oriented gameplay and gives you the freedom to play as you want.</strong><br>                                          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349060/extras/d03f15a4c1ee8c6b5ab9cb9e15c931f2.avif?t=1770948904\" width=640 height=355 /></span>",
